@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ovfnog(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.87)) * (0.45 + 0.53))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.59) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.57)) / ((v0 + 0.11 * v1 + 0.61) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.23)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
